# Bug 1: SSE streaming Connection: keep-alive → hang (benchmark 0/N)
# Bug 2: Non-rank0 worker missing SIGTERM handler → GPU process leak
# Fix: openai_tp_server.py SSE close + os._exit(0) signal handler
